&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The weekend Android Top Gun Development Training Camp has concluded. Over 20 participants enjoyed a nice class by studying and communicating. They’ve learned a lot from the well-designed Android training camp and gave the instructor and the content high marks:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
